# TDLib native libs — vendored under libtd/src/main/libs/<abi>/libtdjni.so.
# These are checked in to the libtd module so a fresh clone builds without
# network. See D-029 (JNI integration replaces the v0.9 ProcessBuilder
# approach, which used a different artifact under app/src/main/jniLibs).
# Note: libtdjni.so is ~65MB total across 4 ABIs; on the edge of GitHub's
# 100MB single-file cap. If we ever need to reduce repo size, we can
# move to a download script + GitHub Release assets (see D-027 history).

